意义。"},"434":{"id":"/blog/cert-8","page_id":"/blog/cert","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/blog/cert#我的思考与困惑","content":"如果传统号码是密码，那网号可以被理解为公钥吗？我们的生物信息作为私钥，二者结合才能完成通信。这么来看，在认证的过程中，似乎安全性提升并不大，传统号码已经采用了多种方式（多因素）来避免身份盗用（例如替考）。"},"435":{"id":"/blog/cert-9","page_id":"/blog/cert","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/blog/cert#我的思考与困惑","content":"我们再来看网号网证的另一个作用，防范信息过度采集。"},"436":{"id":"/blog/cert-10","page_id":"/blog/cert","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/blog/cert#我的思考与困惑","content":"我比较悲观，我觉得在现有的糟糕情况下，网号网证似乎并不能解决它所设想的问题（信息泄露严重），我觉得应该由工信部牵头带领各大互联网平台采取一次混淆数据的活动。（坦白说我也想不到具体的操作方式）"},"437":{"id":"/blog/hello","page_id":"/blog/hello","type":"page","content":"Hello World","tags":[],"url":"/blog/hello"},"438":{"id":"/blog/hello-0","page_id":"/blog/hello","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/blog/hello#hello-world","content":"Hello World"},"439":{"id":"/blog/hello-1","page_id":"/blog/hello","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/blog/hello#hello-world","content":"这是一篇博客示例！"},"440":{"id":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup","page_id":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup","type":"page","content":"如何构建现代化的前端开发环境","tags":[],"url":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup"},"441":{"id":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup-0","page_id":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup","content":"从零开始搭建一个高效的现代前端开发环境，包括工具选择和配置优化。"},"442":{"id":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup-1","page_id":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup#前言","content":"前言"},"443":{"id":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup-2","page_id":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup#核心工具选择","content":"核心工具选择"},"444":{"id":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup-3","page_id":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup#1-包管理器","content":"包管理器"},"445":{"id":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup-4","page_id":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/blog/modern-frontend-setup#2-构建工具","content":"构建工